            <ce:table xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/cals/dtd" frame="topbot" id="t0025" rowsep="0" colsep="0">
               <ce:label>Table 5</ce:label>
               <ce:caption id="cn0035">
                  <ce:simple-para id="sp0050" view="all">Average percentage variation of structural parameters (dPAR) of the models according to forest management system alternatives: from no management (UN) to close to nature (CTN) and to combined objective forestry (CO). Considered forest management systems are based on <ce:cross-ref refid="b0085" id="c0025">Duncker et al. (2012)</ce:cross-ref>. The percentage variation by management system is calculated as average for each structural parameter from the values reported in the main sources.</ce:simple-para>
               </ce:caption>
               <tgroup cols="4">
                  <colspec colname="col1" align="left"/>
                  <colspec colname="col2" align="left"/>
                  <colspec colname="col3" align="left"/>
                  <colspec colname="col4" align="left"/>
