            <ce:table xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/cals/dtd" frame="topbot" id="t0030" rowsep="0" colsep="0">
               <ce:label>Table 6</ce:label>
               <ce:caption id="cn0040">
                  <ce:simple-para id="sp0055" view="all">Estimated effects of standardised tree structural parameters on the occurrence and richness, according to the generalized linear mixed model assuming a binomial distribution (occurrence) or a Poisson error distribution (richness) and tree species as random effects. Significance value: ***(p &lt; 0.001); **(p &lt; 0.01), *(p &lt; 0.05). The dispersion was 0.98 (p-value = 0.77) for occurrence and 0.71 (p-value = 0.03) for richness, according DHARMa nonparametric dispersion test via sd of residuals fitted vs. simulated, alternative hypothesis: two.sided. Number of observations = 1416, groups: Species, 11.</ce:simple-para>
               </ce:caption>
               <tgroup cols="6">
                  <colspec colname="col1" align="left"/>
                  <colspec colname="col2" align="left"/>
                  <colspec colname="col3" align="left"/>
                  <colspec colname="col4" align="left"/>
                  <colspec colname="col5" align="left"/>
                  <colspec colname="col6" align="left"/>
                  <thead>
                     <row rowsep="1" valign="top">
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Structural parameters</entry>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Estimate</entry>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Std. Error</entry>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">z value</entry>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Pr(&gt;|z|)</entry>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd"/>
                     </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                     <row valign="top">
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">
                           <italic>Occurrence model*</italic>
                        </entry>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd"/>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd"/>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd"/>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd"/>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd"/>
                     </row>
                     <row valign="top">
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">Intercept</entry>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">0.633</entry>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">0.235</entry>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">2.694</entry>
                        <entry xmlns="http://www.elsevier.com/xml/common/dtd">0.00707</entry>
